oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Westmoreland Heights flyer
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Westmoreland Heights "Knoxville's Ideal Suburb." Flyer advertising lots available in Westmoreland Heights, Knox County, TN. Plot map on inside pages.; surveyed in 1925. McMillan & Klein, Realtors. Picture on cover of entrance and water wheel. Ephemera 2011.001.
